### W.18 What's clean

- `is_kid_delegated` claim enforcement on refresh is tight â€” adult GoTrue tokens can't rotate into kid tokens (`api/kids/refresh/route.js:67`).
- SupabaseKidsClient bearer-token injection is correct â€” no accidental anon-auth leaks.
