### AA.3 Age gate is checkbox-only

- `signup/page.tsx:660` checkbox: "I confirm I am 13 or older."
- No secondary verification, no parent-pairing flow from the adult signup path.
- Kid ticking the box creates an adult account with adult content access. COPPA-edge.

### AA.4 Pick-username race on simultaneous submit

- Collision check is pre-submit; insert is post-submit.
- Two users submitting same handle at the same instant both see "available" client-side; one hits `23505` on DB insert.
- Narrow but real. UX recovery relies on a generic "try again" rather than surfacing the specific collision.

### AA.5 Reserved-usernames not Unicode-normalized

- `.toLowerCase()` without NFKC normalization.
- `cafÃ©` vs `cafe` treated as distinct handles.
- Lookalike / homoglyph impersonation surface.

### AA.6 Welcome carousel launch-hide tech debt

- 10 `eslint-disable react-hooks/rules-of-hooks` lines across the welcome page for the launch-hide pattern.
